These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, lawyer
1. the accountant is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Sport         | climbing   | badminton |
| Job   | accountant  | lawyer      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, white
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
3. the aristoff-smoker is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
4. the person who likes pink is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Cigar         | aristoff | bolivar   |
| Color   | pink               | white  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
House: victorian, wooden
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, handball
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| House   | victorian       | wooden |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Sport           | climbing        | handball   |

