1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person traveling to miami##8
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | scientific |
| City   | nizza    | miami     |
| Hobby         | board-games  | skydiving    |
| Transport     | scooter     | boat       |

